OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAntarctic-trekking         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fprofessor gets Polar Medal 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An Antarctic-trekking academic has been
OL,6, awarded the Polar Medal.               
OL,8,FProf John Smellie, from the University 
OL,9,Fof Leicester, was given the accolade by
OL,10,FKing Charles III.                      
OL,12,FIt is the second time he has received  
OL,13,Fthe medal, having been awarded one by  
OL,14,FQueen Elizabeth II in 1986.            
OL,16,FThe professor, who spent most of his   
OL,17,Fcareer working as a senior             
OL,18,Fvolcanologist for the British Antarctic
OL,19,FSurvey, said he had been "quite        
OL,20,Fshocked" to receive the honour twice.  
